summary:
Holder of a Law Degree from NOVA School of Law in Lisbon, Portugal, currently a Master’s Student at Maastricht University for International Laws.

Passionate about International and European Law, Diplomacy and Public Policy.

Headed to Bruges in September to study at the College of Europe under a Portuguese Ministry of Foreign Affairs scholarship.
